**Market Analysis of Cannabidiol (CBD) Tea**

The Cannabidiol (CBD) tea market is experiencing significant growth, driven by the increasing awareness of the potential health benefits associated with CBD consumption. CBD-infused products have gained popularity in recent years due to their perceived therapeutic properties, such as stress relief, pain management, and relaxation. The global CBD tea market is expected to witness substantial growth in the coming years, with a CAGR of nan% from 2021 to 2028. The market size was valued at nan million in nan and is projected to reach nan million by nan. Several factors contribute to the growth of the CBD tea market, including the legalization of cannabis in various regions, changing consumer preferences towards natural and organic products, and the rising demand for functional beverages.

